<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<window id="1112">
	<defaultcontrol always="true">100</defaultcontrol>
	<include>Animation_DialogPopupOpenClose</include>
	<depth>DepthDialog+</depth>
	<controls>
		<include>ZeroFadeBackground</include>
		<control type="group">
			<height>700</height>
			<centertop>50%</centertop>
			<centerleft>50%</centerleft>
			<width>1300</width>
			<include content="DialogBackgroundCommons">
				<param name="header_label" value="Welcome to Altus" />
				<param name="header_id" value="1" />
				<param name="header_top" value="15" />
				<param name="divider_top" value="90" />
				<param name="darken_bg" value="false" />
			</include>
			<control type="textbox" id="9">
				<left>40</left>
				<top>100</top>
				<width>1220</width>
				<height>1000</height>
				<textcolor>unfocused_text</textcolor>
				<font>font32</font>
				<label>Pressing OK will set up your home screen.[CR][CR]If you're coming from a previous version of Altus, your existing widget configuration will be migrated automatically.[CR][CR]If this is a fresh install, a default set of sections and widgets will be created for you.[CR][CR]Coming from Nimbus or FENtastic? You can import your widget configuration from Skin Settings > Import from Other Skin.[CR][CR]You can customize everything from Skin Settings > Widget Manager.</label>
				<autoscroll time="3000" delay="4000" repeat="5000">true</autoscroll>
			</control>
			<control type="button" id="100">
				<visible>!Skin.HasSetting(firsttimerun)</visible>
				<centerleft>50%</centerleft>
				<top>570</top>
				<width>219</width>
				<height>70</height>
				<label>OK</label>
				<font>font25_title</font>
				<textoffsetx>20</textoffsetx>
				<onclick>Skin.Setbool(firsttimerun)</onclick>
				<onclick>back</onclick>
				<onclick>RunScript(script.altus.helper,mode=migrate_and_generate)</onclick>
				<align>center</align>
				<aligny>center</aligny>
				<texturefocus border="23" colordiffuse="$VAR[FocusColorTheme]">masks/radius_23.png</texturefocus>
				<texturenofocus border="23" colordiffuse="$VAR[FocusColorTheme]">masks/radius_23_dark.png</texturenofocus>
			</control>
		</control>
	</controls>
</window>
